C programs for basics in writing code :

1. trinum.c -	Program to print first hundred triangular numbers ( -lm should be given at the end of compilation statement for gcc, to include math.h).
2. fact.c -	Program to print factorial of 4 and 5.
3. cmdarg.c -	Program to print given command line arguments using goto and if.
4. oddnum.c - 	Program to print odd numbers between 0 and 10 by seven different ways.
